{"tid":1150063,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想去Thanos 個後花園 應該搭幾號巴士","createTime":"2019-05-11T14:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:29:10.000Z","uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3a39550a81d3edb78cfe90f47a8c5bb197f854","tid":1150063,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e1dc3776b80a26ead25360a2cbbfb83be76b31","tid":1150063,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"傻咗？巴士都去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坐船啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f24419b48cccc517900bdf9781d12f6c8912e1","tid":1150063,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"想入佢後花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227bc65cd45edb16786536e515966dacb1b3d3cc","tid":1150063,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"號外!大家有機會見到Thanos真人<br />\n<br />\n後花園星12天世界平衡之旅(LCNIG424N)<br />\n<br />\n出發日期:2024年(暫定)<br />\n乘搭宇宙級光速飛船，前往編號02595後花園星(詳細地點保密)<br />\n乘搭24小時光速之旅，體驗宇宙跳躍進行時光移動!<br />\n途中經過舊Asgard聖域，觀賞神域毀滅後留下的殘存遺跡<br />\n暢遊當地自然風景區，深入了解花園星的奇特地理面貌<br />\n遊覽後花園星觀光景點；Thanos小屋，享受當地鮮摘的特種大南瓜，體驗一代梟雄的退休生活，並與稻草盔甲留影。<br />\n特別安排與Thanos親身講解對於理想世界以及平衡宇宙的看法，並設有觀眾發問時間(共一小時)。<br />\n旅程結束後能以優惠價購買Thanos最新自傳:我是如果令世界變得更美好的(每人只限一本)<br />\n<br />\n30人成團，現已接受預訂，報名從速每位只需三千萬美金，包來回食宿。<br />\n＊嚴禁攜帶攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"91e096b381a27696c8c25f40230a275555fe9d7b","tid":1150063,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:57:24.000Z","msg":"9527"},{"pid":"f440927fefe4381a721ce48a9d9b1a7e7fb9f3e3","tid":1150063,"uid":36435,"